message.body: Hello quirks
Hello! How are you? Happy July 4 :)
Im okay. Bout to go to a 4th party. How are you?
Aw how nice. I'm fine, but I don't have any fun plans for the day. My parents are visiting! :p
Are you happy about that?
I'd rather be with friends, but yes, it's good to see them even if they're a bit boring.
ears are any indication...
Ahaha sometimes i'd love to have boring...seeing my dade tmrw. lets put it this way, i'd rather wish i'd gone to see him than wish i had not. if past y
aw haha. I hear you. Will your party have fireworks? Hot dogs? Are you in Philly?
Hot dogs and maybe fire works. I am not in philly although my pops lives in sellersville, PA
Sounds good then :). Ah I just asked because it seems like most people in this study live in philly
O yeah? is that where the school that is running this located?
Yep! University of Pennsylvania.
I wonder if its really ab linguistics
I'm pretty sure it is! (Ima linguist too) but that would be super cool if it were a psych experiment about who's more likely to start conversations or something
for monies. Either way chatting like this is fun enough which is a thing hin itself huh
Would it be tho? That is a bit unethical, nO? A friend keeps saying its a DoD thing...maybe im a bot! interesting to is the willingness to ID yourself
Yeah...maybe haha. I don't think I've talked to any bots yet tho. And while it is fun, I wouldn't say no to some monies :p
Right me either...maybe its a study about letting your guard down for some cash youll never see!
A tragic study, for sure! Also sad is the fact that I never get repeated people... I wonder how many participants they have! Must be quite a few.
How long have you been on it? How many people?
Hmm, maybe 3 months or so? So like 90 people
How bout you?
Youre my first
Oh wow!! Sorry to disappoint haha. I think you'll find that a lot of people just don't even respond at all though which is kind of frustrating (unless it
s a glitch or something)
Maybe theyre just occupied
Seen any good movies?
Hmm, not really. Last movie I saw was Star Trek, I think, and it was decent. You?
42. Decent enough.
Saw the purge it was bad
Haha I'm not surprised it looked terrible
It could have been good. Are you w your parents? hangin tough?
Yeah, interesting concept at least. Yep, parents are here! We are going to eat at the local tgi Fridays haha. Are you at the party?
Just left. Had some pork and a beer. Should have had more since it was a chef's party but didnt have too much of an appetite
Ooh. Yeah it's hard for me to be hungry when I'm outside and it's so hot. What're you gonna do now?
Its raining here so its pretty cooool. Might go to a poker after party in a bit.
Sounds nice! Whereabouts are you? I'm in Delaware, it's been raining for weeks but its super hot bla
Ew raining and hot we get so much of that in FL
And bugs!!! D:
